<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078645" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Incomparabili, et Celeberrimo D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Johanni Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></salute></opener>
<p>Tandem maximo cum gaudio tuam accepi <rs key="B_991170515020205501" type="letter">epistolam</rs> 18<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice><hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<lb/>huius Mensis Julii <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">istic</rs> conscriptam, et per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs> ad me
                   <lb/>transmissam. Ex eadem epistola intellexi Vir Doctissime
                   <lb/>rationes, ob quas Agnati tui <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolai</rs> Viri Clarissimi, et
                   <lb/>tui <rs key="B_991170515020505501" type="letter">litter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Dem <rs key="B_991170517053905501" type="letter">Brief von Nikolaus I Bernoulli an Michelotti</rs> lag ein weiterer Brief von Johann I Bernoulli bei. Sie wurden beide am 15. Mai 1714 verfasst.</note> 15 Ma<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> exarat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me non pervenerant. Do<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>leo plurimum quod perierint; verum tamen fieri potest ut
                   <lb/>aliquando ad meas perveniant manus. Quicquid sit, li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bentissime tuam voluntatem ex <rs key="B_991170515020205501" type="letter">hac ultima tua episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>la</rs> deduxi in eo quod spectat Mathematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs>
<lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavinam</rs>. Salarium 1500 thalerorum imperialium
                   <lb/>quod petivisti si ad tuam incomparabilem Personam
                   <lb/>respiciamus perexiguum quidem est; si ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> illud <choice><sic>ref<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ere</sic><corr>referre</corr></choice> velimus ad salaria qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> solent Professoribus
                   <lb/>eximiis <rs type="organisation">Archilycei Patavini</rs> exhibere isti <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rend="sup">i</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deratores</rs>, revera illud est plusquam maximum. Ego in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>genu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> tibi testor neminem cuiuscunque scienti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fessorem vocatum fuisse <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs> cum exhibi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tione Salarii, quod tibi exhibebunt (si <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavium</rs>
<lb/>venire non recusabis) <choice><abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimi</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Ex.<hi rend="sup">mi</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs>; qui
                   <lb/>maximum ostendunt desiderium te utpote Maximum
                   <lb/>Mathematicum promovendi. Si salarium non recu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sas cito promoveberis, et docebis solum per trienni<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                   <lb/>deinde tui loco sine u<choice><orig><g ref="#ll">ƚ</g></orig><reg>ll</reg></choice>o dubio promovebitur <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pos</rs> tuus <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs>, qui <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> quousque
                   <lb/>ipsi lubebit permanebit docendo cum Stipendio,
                   <lb/>quod quolibet triennio crescet. Maximum salarium
                   <pb facs="1078646" n="1v"/>
<lb/>quod obtinere poteris quolibet anno ab hac <choice><abbr>Sereniss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr><expan>Serenissima</expan></choice>
<lb/>et <choice><abbr>Potentiss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi></abbr><expan>Potentissima</expan></choice> <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Republica</rs> erit 1200 florenorum. Scias
                   <lb/>autem unum ex his florenis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalere plusquam
                   <lb/>dimidi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> unci<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> argenti, sive ad florenum germani<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cum eam habere rationem im<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> paulisper ma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>iorem quam 6 ad 5; ideoque dimidio thalero im<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>periali non parum esse maiorem: H<choice><orig><g ref="#ihat">î</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice>c enim thale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rus imperialis non <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quivalet unci<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> integr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> huius
                   <lb/>argenti. Huiusmodi autem stipendium (si velles
                   <lb/>etiam post triennium docere) cresceret: si au<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem docere amplius noles promovebitur certissime
                   <lb/>ad tuum locum implendum <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> Nepos tuus
                   <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus</rs>. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum scias te posse vivere <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavi<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs> sine
                   <lb/>magno, victum quod attinet, dispendio: et quem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>admodum lectiones public<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> desinunt versus finem
                   <lb/>Mensis Iunii, et vacationes sequuntur absolut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> usque
                   <lb/>ad primam aut 2.<hi rend="sup">dam</hi> diem Mensis Novembris,
                   <lb/>ita per totum vacationum tempus poteris
                   <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetias</rs> te conferre, et in Domo mea habitare abs<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que ullo habitationis, victus, aut alterius rei dispen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dio; cubile etenim domi me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erit tibi paratum,
                   <lb/>victum tibi gratis subministrabo, et tota
                   <lb/>cum libertate poteris mecum commorari; quod
                   <lb/>summum mihi erit decus, et maximum sola
                 <pb facs="1078647" n="2r"/>
<lb/>men: quandoquidem scientias sublimiores mathematicas,
                   <lb/>et Mechanicen pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> horis vacuis si tibi placebit
                   <lb/>a te perdiscam licet easdem iampridem didicerim
                   <lb/>iisdemque, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter Medicin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> studium, sim valde ad<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dictus.</p>
<p>Ego itaque te hortor, et deprecor ut hoc salarium
                   <lb/>valde honorificum, et quod nemini ante te fuit
                   <lb/>oblatum, non recuses potissimum cum conditione
                   <lb/>docendi per triennium tantum, et poste<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> substi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tuendi ad eandem <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> tuum,
                   <lb/>quem ego maximi facio.</p>
<p>Ut tibi verum fatear, <choice><abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr><expan>Clarissimus</expan></choice> Agnatus tuus non
                   <lb/>promovebitur nisi tu conditionibus pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dictis digna<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>beris Patavinam Provinciam amplecti per trien<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nium. H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c est voluntas horum <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimorum</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>deratorum</rs>, apud quos sicuti tuum nomen magni
                   <lb/>fit ita <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nepotis</rs> fama etsi a me quotidi<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> sum<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mis laudibus et quidem iustissimis exornata, non
                   <lb/>magna est, ob malevolos, et eiusdem inimicos, qui
                   <lb/>Mathematum <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> etsi ipso inferio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>res exoptant. Mea officia apud hosce <choice><abbr>Illus.<hi rend="sup">os</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimos</expan></choice>
<lb/>et <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">os</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimos</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatores</rs> valent obtinere id quod
                   <lb/>ex hac mea <rs key="B_991170515020005501" type="letter">epistola</rs> intelligis; qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> adhuc te
                   <lb/>exhortor, et precor ut stipendium conditionibus obla<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<pb facs="1078648" n="2v"/><lb break="no"/>tis non recuses si cupis ut <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatus</rs> tuus promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>veatur; etenim nisi per hanc viam incedamus ipse
                   <lb/>non promovebitur uti pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>video.</p>
<p>H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c tibi habebam dicenda pro Te et Agnato tuo
         <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao</rs>, cui ut communices velim h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
         <lb/>in hac mea <rs key="B_991170515020005501" type="letter">epistola</rs> continentur, et salutem plurimam
         <lb/>meo nomine dicas.</p>
<p>Maximum mihi impertietis favorem si <rs key="biblio_W6BHQDM2 biblio_I2Z37CBH biblio_RTB4565Q biblio_WPXENY2H" type="biblio">scripta</rs> maxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mi facienda, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te, et ab immortali fratre
                   <lb/>tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Iacobo</rs> iampridem edita fuere, un<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> cum <rs key="biblio_69NKSR46" type="biblio">aureo
                      <lb/>libello <rs key="pers_DE-588-117601020" type="person"><choice><abbr>Mont.<hi rend="sup">ii</hi></abbr><expan>Montmortii</expan></choice></rs></rs> transmittetis <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">Bergomum</rs>
<lb/>ad <choice><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimum</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimum</expan></choice> D. Comitem Carolum <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089631200" type="person">Zeno<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bium</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3182164" type="place">illius Urbis</rs> Capitaneum.</p>
<p>Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tere<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me plurimum tibi obstrictum habebis si
                   <lb/>tuam methodum mihi communicabis dimetiendi
                   <lb/>fluida crassiora, et subtiliora, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> facile possim di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gnoscere quid mathematic<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> loquendo sit fluidum
                   <lb/>crassum, quid fluidum subtile; et quare unum
                   <lb/>fluidum altero crassius, aut subtilius dicatur secun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dum rigorem mathematicum.</p>
<p>Tandem te rogo ut quamprimum poteris <rs key="B_991170515019905501" type="letter">responsum</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli antwortet Michelotti in seinem Brief vom 15. August 1714.</note>
<lb/>ad me mittas per <rs key="place_VER-tirola" type="place">Tyrolim</rs>, pro hac mea <rs key="B_991170515020005501" type="letter">epistola</rs>, ut
                   <lb/>aliquid possim dicere de tuo adventu coram <choice><abbr>Nobiliss.<hi rend="sup">is</hi></abbr><expan>Nobilissimis</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="person">Moderatoribus</rs>.</p>
<closer><salute>Vale Vir celeberrime, scias<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me valde
